narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend taking this course in the fall of your senior year. Although it isn't necessary, I'd recommend starting to think about your topic in the summer.

A 25-30 page essay that every HSAR major must complete. This is a largely unstructured project for which you must create your own organizational system. Choose a topic you think you would enjoy, though make sure you can formulate clever questions about it. Turn in drafts early and ask your advisor to look at them several times. Good luck on the long, sometimes grueling process.
